INSERT INTO `content` VALUES (1,1,'page','published','2010-10-14 17:19:37','2011-03-01 07:53:02',1,'home','Home','<h1>	The difference is night and day</h1><h3>	A new prescription treatment for obstructive sleep apnea (OSA)</h3><p>	<span class=\"st_sharethis\" displaytext=\"ShareThis\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://www.proventtherapy.com/images/space.gif\" width=\"1\" /></span></p><p>	Now, there&rsquo;s a new alternative to CPAP that is proven to effectively treat Obstructive Sleep Apnea and related snoring, and can restore the energy that comes with a good night&#39;s sleep. The Provent Nasal Device is small, hassle-free, and powered by your own breathing, so it requires no mask or machine. The device is available by prescription only and is FDA-cleared for the treatment of OSA.</p><p>	Provent Therapy is a clinically proven obstructive sleep apnea treatment and is effective for mild, moderate, and severe OSA. So if you&rsquo;re looking for an OSA solution that fits your lifestyle and improves sleep quality, making you feel more alert and focused, this could be your dream come true.</p><p>	<strong><a href=\"http://www.proventtherapy.com/about_provent\">Learn more about how Provent Therapy treats obstructive sleep apnea.</a></strong></p><h3>	A CPAP alternative</h3><p>	This new treatment for obstructive sleep apnea uses the power of your own breathing to create expiratory positive airway pressure (EPAP) to restore natural airflow. Its innovative nasal MicroValve technology is effective, and unlike CPAP therapy, the Provent device is discreet, portable, and easy to use. Compared to CPAP, Provent Therapy:</p><ul>	<li>		Is small enough to slip into a purse or pocket, making it ideal for travel</li>	<li>		Does not require a machine or make noise, allowing you and your partner to sleep better together</li>	<li>		Does not require electricity, giving you the freedom to use it anywhere</li>	<li>		Is simple, comfortable, and maintenance-free; you use a fresh set every night</li></ul><p>	<strong><a href=\"http://www.proventtherapy.com/why_provent_therapy\">Find out more about how Provent Therapy could be the solution for you.</a></strong></p><h3>	A solution to reduce snoring</h3><p>	Snoring is a troubling symptom of obstructive sleep apnea and can disrupt your sleep and your relationship with your partner. Provent Therapy works by keeping your airway open, reducing vibration in the restricted airway that causes the snoring. This can mean better sleep for you and a more peaceful sleep experience for your partner.</p><p>	<strong><a href=\"http://www.proventtherapy.com/benefits\">Learn more about other benefits associated with PROVENT Therapy.</a></strong></p>',0,0,'home.template.php'),
