(36,1,'page','published','2011-01-26 12:19:15','2011-03-01 05:22:58',0,'a_proven_alternative_to_cpap','A Proven Alternative to CPAP','<p>	<img alt=\"Provent Therapy couple\" src=\"http://www.proventtherapy.com/images/land_cpap.png\" style=\"width: 460px; height: 305px\" /></p><p>	This new treatment for obstructive sleep apnea uses the power of your own breathing to create expiratory positive airway pressure (EPAP) to restore natural airflow. Its innovative MicroValve technology is effective, and unlike CPAP therapy, the Provent device is discreet, portable, and easy to use.</p>',0,0,'cpap_one.template.php'),
(37,1,'page','published','2011-01-26 12:19:50','2011-03-01 05:23:14',0,'fda_cleared_for_the_treatment_of_obstructive_sleep_apnea__osa_','FDA Cleared for the Treatment of Obstructive Sleep Apnea (OSA)','<p>	<img alt=\"Provent Therapy couple\" src=\"http://www.proventtherapy.com/images/land_sleep.png\" style=\"width: 460px; height: 305px\" /></p><p>	There is no non-invasive cure for obstructive sleep apnea. Untreated OSA is associated with a number of serious conditions, including high blood pressure, heart attack, stroke, diabetes and depression. Provent Therapy is a new treatment for OSA. Studies have shown that treating OSA can reduce associated health risks.</p>',0,0,'problems_one.template.php'),
(38,1,'page','published','2011-01-26 12:23:15','2011-03-01 05:23:28',0,'good_sleep__good_morning__good_day_','Good Sleep. Good Morning. Good Day.','<p>	<img alt=\"Provent Therapy\" src=\"http://www.proventtherapy.com/images/land_apnea.png\" style=\"width: 460px; height: 305px\" /></p><div>	Provent Therapy is a new treatment for obstructive sleep apnea. Studies have shown that treating OSA can reduce associated health risks (like depression and heart disease).</div>',0,0,'apnea_one.template.php'),
